## 5. 错误处理与验证

### 5.1 断言模式

**使用 `check()` 处理内部不变量:**
```cpp
check(InASCToGive);
check(AbilityTagToActive.IsValid());
check(TargetASC && InSpecHandle.IsValid());
```

**使用 `checkf()` 并附带描述性消息处理配置错误:**
```cpp
checkf(InputConfigDataAsset, TEXT("Forgot to assign a valid data asset as input config"));
checkf(WeaponOwingPawn, TEXT("Forgot to assign an instigator as the owning pawn for the weapon: %s"), *GetName());
checkf(!CharacterCarriedWeaponMap.Contains(Tag), TEXT("A named %s has already been added as carried weapon"), *Tag.ToString());
```

**使用 `ensureMsgf()` 处理可恢复的错误:**
```cpp
ensureMsgf(!CharacterStartUpData.IsNull(), TEXT("Forgot to assign star up data to %s"), *GetName());
```

### 5.2 有效性检查

```cpp
// Tag 有效性
if (!InInputTag.IsValid()) return;

// 软对象引用
if (CharacterStartUpData.IsNull()) return;

// 弱指针
if (!CachedWarriorHeroCharacter.IsValid()) { /* 重新缓存 */ }

// 数组为空
if (InDefaultWeaponAbilities.IsEmpty()) return;
```

